<div class="param-panneau" id="panneau-securite">
    <div class="dash-card mb-3">
        <p class="param-section-titre">Mot de passe</p>
        <div class="row g-3">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <label class="form-label" for="mdp-actuel">Mot de passe actuel</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="mdp-actuel" autocomplete="current-password" placeholder="••••••••" data-navigation-optional>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <label class="form-label" for="mdp-nouveau">Nouveau mot de passe</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="mdp-nouveau" autocomplete="new-password" placeholder="8 caractères minimum" data-navigation-optional>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
                <label class="form-label" for="mdp-confirme">Confirmation</label>
                <input type="password" class="form-control" id="mdp-confirme" autocomplete="new-password" placeholder="Retapez le mot de passe" data-navigation-optional>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-dash-ghost mt-3" type="button">
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="10" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 10V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v3"/></svg>
            Mettre à jour le mot de passe
        </button>
        <p class="param-section-titre">Double authentification</p>
        <div class="ligne-switch">
            <span class="ligne-switch__icone"><svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-3.5 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6.5 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg></span>
            <div><b>Validation en deux étapes (2FA)</b><p>Code de confirmation par SMS à chaque nouvelle connexion.</p></div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch"><input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" role="switch" id="securite-2fa" checked aria-label="Validation en deux étapes (2FA)"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="param-section-titre">Sessions actives</p>
        {% for session in sessions %}
            {% set est_courante = session.sessionToken == currentSessionToken %}
            <div class="session">
                            <span class="session__icone">
                            {% if 'iPhone' in session.deviceLabel or 'iPad' in session.deviceLabel or 'Android' in session.deviceLabel %}
                                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="7" y="2" width="10" height="20" rx="2"/><path d="M11 18h2"/></svg>
                            {% else %}
                                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
                            {% endif %}
                            </span>
                <div>
                    <b>{{ session.deviceLabel }}{% if est_courante %} <span class="chip chip--accepte">CET APPAREIL</span>{% endif %}</b>
                    <p>
                        {{ session.city ?? 'Localisation inconnue' }}{% if session.countryCode %}, {{ session.countryCode }}{% endif %}
                        · Dernière activité : {{ session.lastActivityAt|ago }}
                    </p>
                </div>
                {% if not est_courante %}
                    <button class="btn btn-dash-ghost btn-sm" type="button">Déconnecter</button>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        {% else %}
            <div class="session"><div><p>Aucune session active.</p></div></div>
        {% endfor %}


    </div>
    <div class="zone-danger">
        <b><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3 2 20h20z"/><path d="M12 10v4M12 17h.01"/></svg> Zone sensible</b>
        <p>La suppression de votre compte est définitive : profil public, avis, devis et historique seront effacés après un délai légal de 30 jours. Votre abonnement en cours ne sera pas remboursé.</p>
        <button class="btn-danger-ghost" type="button">Supprimer mon compte professionnel</button>
    </div>
</div>
